* Review of mechanical ITP, MS and Commissioning Plans in collaboration with RINA engineering team;
* On site inspections following the agreed ITPs and check lists;
* Monitor all QA/QC related issues (e.g. issuing and following Non Conformities or Inspection tasks) related to the mechanical systems of the Buildings;
